intent: |
  A reset of product strategy: market view, competitor landscape, portfolio bets, multi-year roadmap,
  and updated north-star. Published artefact replaces the prior strategy memo.

scope: |
  A reset of product strategy: market view, competitor landscape, portfolio bets, multi-year roadmap,
  and updated north-star. Published artefact replaces the prior strategy memo.

summary: |
  A reset of product strategy: market view, competitor landscape, portfolio bets, multi-year roadmap,
  and updated north-star. Published artefact replaces the prior strategy memo.

